  <metadata>
    <name>Hong Kong Climbing &amp; Bouldering Sites (90)</name>
    <desc>Waypoint collection of 90 outdoor rock-climbing and bouldering areas (no gyms). Names from hongkongclimbing.com and thecrag.com; coordinates cross-validated against thecrag.com, thetopo.com and OpenStreetMap; some waypoints mark the approach/access point rather than the rock itself. Elevations bilinear-sampled from the HK Lands Department 5 m LiDAR DTM (Hong Kong Principal Datum).</desc>
    <time>2026-07-02T13:43:59Z</time>
    <link href="https://hongkongclimbing.com/">
      <text>Hong Kong Climbing</text>
    </link>
